    <owl:Class rdf:about="https://socialcaredata.github.io/ontology/placements#QualityAssurance">
        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">Metadata about who recorded each part of the placement record (referral, placement, cost) and when. Supports LA-internal review of data-entry practices; not intended to be shared beyond the recording LA.</rdfs:comment>
